Overview
===========
This is an app to play Rock-Paper-Scissors (a.k.a, "じゃんけん" in Japanese).  

Application description
=======================
With this application, you can play Rock-Paper-Scissors based on the following rules.

* You can play each hand (rock, paper, and scissors) a maximum of 10 times
* Opponent hands are provided by http://example.com/randhand as number strings.
    * 0, 1, and 2 represents rock, paper, and scissors respectively.
    * The server is not reliable. It sometimes replies with an invalid value.
    * (This server does not actually exist.)

If there is an error, this application must report to http://example.com/randhand.  

